ily: 宋体\">1.<span style=\";padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\";padding: 0px;font-family: 宋体\">安装PPT2010或以上版本。太低的版本可能会没办法保存成视频格式哦。</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 24px;padding: 0px;float: left;width: 789px;line-height: 28px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Trebuchet MS&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif;white-space: normal\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;font-family: 宋体\">2.<span style=\";padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\";padding: 0px;font-family: 宋体\">准备好一份PPT。PPT的标题和内容，需要精心设计，并且在PPT里做好动画，待用。</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 24px;padding: 0px;float: left;width: 789px;line-height: 28px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Trebuchet MS&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif;white-space: normal\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;font-family: 宋体\">3.<span style=\";padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\";padding: 0px;font-family: 宋体\">插入耳麦、话筒，或者直接使用笔记本的话筒，保证录音设备能够正常使用即可。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;float: left;width: 789px;line-height: 28px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Trebuchet MS&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif;white-space: normal\"><strong style=\";padding: 0px\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;font-family: 宋体\"><br style=\";padding: 0px\"/></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;float: left;width: 789px;line-height: 28px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Trebuchet MS&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif;white-space: normal\"><strong style=\";padding: 0px\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;font-family: 宋体\">第二步，视频录制</span></strong></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 24px;padding: 0px;float: left;width: 789px;line-height: 28px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Trebuchet MS&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif;white-space: normal\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;font-family: 宋体\">1.<span style=\";padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\";padding: 0px;font-family: 宋体\">打开你准备的PPT，动画的播放方式，可根据个人喜好，设置成自动放映或鼠标点击放映。</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 24px;padding: 0px;float: left;width: 789px;line-height: 28px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Trebuchet MS&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif;white-space: normal\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;font-family: 宋体\">2.<span style=\";padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\";padding: 0px;font-family: 宋体\">选择【幻灯片放映】，在弹出下方功能菜单中，选择【录制幻灯片演示】，【从头开始录制】。</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 24px;padding: 0px;float: left;width: 789px;line-height: 28px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Trebuchet MS&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif;white-space: normal\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;font-family: 宋体\">3.<span style=\";padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\";padding: 0px;font-family: 宋体\">在弹出框里，勾选“幻灯片和动画计时”，第二个可选可不选。选好后，点击开始录制按钮。</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 24px;padding: 0px;float: left;width: 789px;line-height: 28px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Trebuchet MS&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif;white-space: normal\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;font-family: 宋体\">4.<span style=\";padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\";padding: 0px;font-family: 宋体\">点击开始录制后，会出现一个时间进度控制条，先来熟悉一下吧。这里包括“下一页”“暂停”“重复”“总计时”，你可以点击暂停按钮暂停录制，也可以点击下一项到下一页PPT。5</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 24px;padding: 0px;float: left;width: 789px;line-height: 28px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Trebuchet MS&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif;white-space: normal\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;font-family: 宋体\">5.<span style=\";padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\";padding: 0px;font-family: 宋体\">熟悉功能之后，你可以开始演讲了。你可以用鼠标滚轮或键盘上的上下键翻至下一页。演示完毕，按键盘上的【ESC】</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;float: left;width: 789px;line-height: 28px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Trebuchet MS&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif;white-space: normal\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;font-family: 宋体\"><br style=\";padding: 0px\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;float: left;width: 789px;line-height: 28px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Trebuchet MS&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif;white-space: normal\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;font-family: 宋体\">以上就是小编给大家分享的PPT录制微课的方法，你学会了么？</span></p><p><br/></p>', '', '', '/media/photos/201803/0/312/original/f057283f5f8cea21f6147a2015468903.jpg', '', '2018-03-28 14:33:30', '2018-03-28 14:33:30'),
(20, 'chi', 6, '测试编辑器', '11', '', '', '<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">培训费：</strong><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">500元 &nbsp;VIP：680元，获得与大咖共享晚餐机会！</span><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;font-size:16px\"><strong>授课导师</strong>：许育忠</span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;font-size:16px\">开课时间：待定</span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;font-size:16px\">地址：汇人商学院静安中心（中山北路756号达人湾117B教室）</span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: small; white-space: nowrap;\"><strong>演讲大纲：</strong></span><br/></p><p><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;font-size:12px\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;font-size:12px\">1、企业文化解决什么问题</span></p><ol><li><p><span style=\"font-size:12px\">做对的事+把事做对<br/></span></p></li><li><p><span style=\"font-size:12px\">能力+意愿<br/></span></p></li><li><p><span style=\"font-size:12px\">生命周期+规模<br/></span></p></li></ol><p><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;font-size:12px\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;font-size:12px\">2、如何形成企业文化的系统化视角</span></p><ul><li><p><span style=\"font-size:12px\">从虚到实的落地路径<br/></span></p></li><li><p><span style=\"font-size:12px\">与其他管理模块的协同<br/></span></p></li></ul><p><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;font-size:12px\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;font-size:12px\">3、如何进行企业文化工作的年度规划</span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;font-size:12px\">主线</span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;font-size:12px\">里程碑</span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;font-size:12px\">运营日历</span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;font-size:12px\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"